  "body": "![Title](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4211e92e4d3dad974bfb75b808840bec893c31c5.png)\n\n  <p align=\"center\">\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/CdHqyDxMrz\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/54/b0/5b/54b05bb9f6d4571a9e7c7206d7e2915b.jpg\" \n       alt=\"Discord PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@wanders_test3?_r=1&_t=ZS-92GITAsLf6u\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/07/87/a6/0787a626098d272cd5b9404828fcfcac.jpg\" \n       alt=\"TikTok PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/@wh_test3?si=5hFPFQdpltcC-8oX\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/74/97/29/7497291420cdd0ae60e5931d97b54549.jpg\" \n       alt=\"YouTube PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/whxzz._?igsh=aG85NjQxZHEzdnZ0\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/cf/df/4b/cfdf4be37a4df24dcf01d9459c200de8.jpg\" \n       alt=\"Instagram PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://m.twitch.tv/wanders_test3/home\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/20/47/ca/2047ca86a5fbadc3d72a4b3222b4914f.jpg\" \n       alt=\"Twitch PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://x.com/Wanders_test3\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/7a/84/57/7a845743f2d491e486b25c2d7c381d3f.jpg\" \n       alt=\"X PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/user/31b6v5kemoxe7cx242v2svghomja?si=_A_qQj61QDC2JtByRrV8tw\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/7e/af/5d/7eaf5d0650b600a298d6692e1092f95c.jpg\" \n       alt=\"Spotify PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://github.com/WandersTest3\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/5a/89/1e/5a891eb9dc9d77c6ea517f21de0104ae.jpg\" \n       alt=\"GitHub PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\nThis RP uses core shaders so Minecraft can use hardcore hearts instead of normal ones, meaning it's compatible with other resource packs, allowing the use of hardcore hearts from other RPs.\n\nThis RP originated [on this GitHub page](https://github.com/McTsts/mc-core-shaders) and after several tests and adjustments, it's available for download in an organized way here.\n\n  <p align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/146981a830769d2a6661b1d49b33f4cfdf31f817.png\" alt=\"important!\" width=\"275\">\n    \n### *If you find any type of bug or error, report it on my [discord server!](https://discord.gg/CdHqyDxMrz)*",
